questionsAndAnswers.question: I am ready to purchase! What do I need to get started?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: You would need a domain name and a hosting account (if you don't have these I will be happy to assist you).I will also need your logo (optional), names & no. of pages, a few sentences about your website/company, e-mail address to configure form.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Will you provide Premium theme with my choice?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Yes, I will provide Premium Theme. those themes are awesome for all kinds of website. if you want another theme then you can buy first and provide me to develop

questionsAndAnswers.question: Do you upload the website on my hosting to make it live?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: YES. I will do it if you provide your Hosting Control Panel before starting the order.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Will you provide Premium theme with my choice?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Yes, I will provide Divi & My Theme shop premium theme. those themes are awesome for all kinds of website. if you want another theme then you can buy first and provide me to develop

questionsAndAnswers.question: I have no ready text and images. what can i do?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: No problem. I can develop your website by dummy text & images. after completing the website, you can change this text & images anytime.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Is there A music player included
Can I add register to download feature?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Yes, It can be made to restrict downloading only to registered users.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Will I Be Able To Update My Website? I do not know programming.
questionsAndAnswers.answer: You will be able to update your website easily using the Control panel offered by Wordpress. You can easily add text & images to all pages, e-commerce products, their images, descriptions & prices and add unlimited pages and posts too. No programming skills required at all.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Will you write the content for the website?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Sorry, but I don't write content, so I recommend you find someone here on Fiverr who can do this. I can only upload the content that you send me.

questionsAndAnswers.question: What happens if I lose my website?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: I will give you the full website back up at the time of delivery your website. You can restore your website from this backup. if you can't do this, I will help you to do this.
